  "title": "Intricately Spiced Egyptian Chicken Bake",
  "description": "This herbal and springy Egyptian dish features coconut cream and is baked to perfection in a molcajete, making it a crowd-pleaser, and is Whole30-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
